{
  "texts": [
    "In 2019 Kather et al. [35] (Fig.",
    "2a) were able to predict MSI in colorectal, gastric, and endometrial cancers.",
    "As a following publication, Echle et al. [36] (Fig.",
    "2a) trained models to predict MSI in colorectal cancer, along with the driver mutations BRAF and KRAS, in larger patient cohorts.",
    "Today, some of these approaches have been implemented by commercial entities and are being marketed as algorithms for routine clinical use in Europe [37]."
  ]
}